      "message": "I\u0027m planning to replace (chan Output) with an interface.\n\nCurrently chan Output is used like an interface in a sense that the testing package can call into its caller (the bundle package) without importing it. I found that using the channel is inconvenient in many aspects, e.g. callers must start a goroutine to handle outputs, difficult to generalize testing.Run, which runs a single test, to a function that runs multiple tests at once. So I\u0027m trying to replace it with an interface, and it will make the whole structure of test execution clearer.",
